  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the effect of blisibimod plus standard of care versus
      placebo plus standard of care alone on the proportion of subjects achieving improvement in
      renal disease parameters.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
